---
title: Pulled Chicken & Bacon Raviolini with Basil Pesto & Leek
description: This raviolini is a firework of flavour! A creamy chicken, bacon and leek sauce wraps around raviolini filled with pumpkin, sundried tomato and feta. Basil pesto and lemon zest stirred through at the end add the perfect punch.
